solution: select distinct t3.name from country as t1 join countrylanguage as t2 on t1.code  =  t2.countrycode join city as t3 on t1.code  =  t3.countrycode where t2.isofficial  =  't' and t2.language  =  'chinese' and t1.continent  =  "asia"
answer: SELECT DISTINCT T1.Name FROM city AS T1 INNER JOIN country AS T2 ON T1.CountryCode = T2.Code INNER JOIN countrylanguage AS T3 ON T2.Code = T3.CountryCode WHERE T2.Continent = 'Asia' AND T3.IsOfficial = 'T' AND T3.Language = 'Chinese'
